Motion design is everywhere. From the title credits on the last blockbuster you saw to the tiny app notification on your smartphone. It enhances the user experience on a website, it helps the narrative of a story, it sets up the mood of a film. But motion design without a purpose becomes noise.

Touet is me, Juan Claramunt, a Freelancer Motion Designer who loves helping people tell their stories. Not only with beautiful visuals but with a purpose to it.

Motion Design comes in many flavors. Complex 3D scenes, 2D cartoon animations, subtle transitions of on screen elements... Finding the best one that fits in your project can sometimes be difficult. Let me help you find the best way to create the most engaging and memorable experience for your project.
